Name: ret_6_1
definition: ratio of cumulative stock returns from the previous month to the cumulative stock returns lagged 6 months (i.e. 6 months ago).

Name: ret_12_1
definition: ratio of cumulative stock returns from the previous month to the cumulative stock returns lagged 1 year (i.e 1 year ago).

Name: prc_highprc_252d
definition: ratio of current stock price of the highest stock price over the past year

Name: resff3_6_1
definition: Residual momentum (error term in Fama-French 3-factor model) over the past 6 months

Name: resff3_12_1
definition: Residual momentum (error term in Fama-French 3-factor model) over the past year

Name: seas_1_1na
definition: Average stock return over the period of 11 months ago to 1 month ago.

Name: ret_3_1
definition: ratio of cumulative stock returns from the previous month to the cumulative stock returns lagged 3 months (i.e. 3 months ago).

Name: ret_9_1
definition: ratio of cumulative stock returns from the previous month to the cumulative stock returns lagged 9 months (i.e. 9 months ago).
